---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="Catering Journal Vancouver | Indian Catering Insights & Guides | Sula"
	description="Insights, guides, and stories from Sula's fifteen years catering Vancouver. Wedding planning, halal catering, corporate lunch ideas, and chai vs coffee."
	canonical="/blog"
>

	<Fragment slot="schema">
		<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
			"@context": "https://schema.org","@type": "Blog",
			"name": "Sula Catering Journal",
			"author": {"@id": "https://sulacatering.com/#organization"}
		})} />
	</Fragment>

	<section class="hero" style="min-height:55vh;background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(20,8,16,0.85) 0%, rgba(38,14,38,0.7) 50%, rgba(20,8,16,0.9) 100%), url('https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Indian-food-catering-vancouver-bc-canada.webp');">
		<div class="hero-content">
			<h1>The <em>Journal</em></h1>
			<p class="hero-tagline">Stories, guides, and insights from fifteen years catering Vancouver's finest events.</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="intro-block reveal">
				<h2>Catering Wisdom, <em>Written Down</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament"><span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span></div>
				<p>Practical guidance and stories from our kitchen — wedding planning, halal certification, corporate lunch ideas, and the small details that make events memorable. Whether you're booking <a href="/weddings" class="body-link">wedding catering</a>, organising <a href="/corporate" class="body-link">corporate lunches</a>, planning a <a href="/private-parties" class="body-link">private party</a>, or curious about <a href="/cafe-catering" class="body-link">café catering</a> — start here.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="blog-grid">
				<a href="/blog/indian-wedding-catering-vancouver-guide" class="blog-card reveal">
					<div class="blog-card-img"><img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/WEDDING.jpg" alt="Indian wedding catering Vancouver guide" loading="lazy" /></div>
					<div class="blog-card-content">
						<p class="blog-card-meta">Wedding Planning · 8 min</p>
						<h3>Indian Wedding Catering: <em>Vancouver's Complete Guide</em></h3>
						<p>Sangeet menus, halal certification, dietary planning, timeline coordination — everything we wish every couple knew before booking.</p>
						<span class="read-more">Read the Guide →</span>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/blog/office-catering-vancouver-large-groups" class="blog-card reveal delay-100">
					<div class="blog-card-img"><img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/office-catering-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Office catering Vancouver large groups" loading="lazy" /></div>
					<div class="blog-card-content">
						<p class="blog-card-meta">Corporate Catering · 6 min</p>
						<h3>Office Catering Vancouver: <em>Feeding 50+ at Work</em></h3>
						<p>Practical guidance on planning a large office lunch — guest count, dietary needs, delivery logistics, menu strategy.</p>
						<span class="read-more">Read More →</span>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/blog/halal-indian-catering-vancouver" class="blog-card reveal delay-200">
					<div class="blog-card-img"><img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Indian-food-catering-vancouver-burnaby-richmond.webp" alt="Halal Indian catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" /></div>
					<div class="blog-card-content">
						<p class="blog-card-meta">Catering Essentials · 5 min</p>
						<h3>Halal Indian <em>Catering Vancouver</em></h3>
						<p>What halal certification means, how to ask the right questions, and why it matters for multi-cultural events.</p>
						<span class="read-more">Read More →</span>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/blog/best-indian-dishes-corporate-lunches" class="blog-card reveal delay-300">
					<div class="blog-card-img"><img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/best-chicken-tikka-masala-vancouver.webp" alt="Best Indian dishes corporate lunches" loading="lazy" /></div>
					<div class="blog-card-content">
						<p class="blog-card-meta">Menu Planning · 4 min</p>
						<h3>Best Indian Dishes for <em>Corporate Lunches</em></h3>
						<p>The crowd-pleasers that always work — butter chicken, paneer butter masala, dal makhani, biryani.</p>
						<span class="read-more">Read More →</span>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/blog/chai-coffee-catering-weddings" class="blog-card reveal">
					<div class="blog-card-img"><img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/masala-chai-sula-indian-restaurant.webp" alt="Chai coffee catering weddings Vancouver" loading="lazy" /></div>
					<div class="blog-card-content">
						<p class="blog-card-meta">Beverage Catering · 5 min</p>
						<h3>Chai vs Coffee: <em>Why Both Belong at Your Wedding</em></h3>
						<p>Building the perfect beverage program for your wedding — from masala chai bars to specialty espresso stations.</p>
						<span class="read-more">Read More →</span>
					</div>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="cta-section">
		<div class="reveal">
			<h2>Ready to Plan Your <em>Event?</em></h2>
			<p>Tell us about your event. We'll respond within 24 hours with a custom menu and quote.</p>
			<a href="https://sulaindianrestaurant.com/request-a-quote/" class="btn btn-gold">Request a Quote</a>
		</div>
	</section>

</Layout>
